'LIGHTBAR' IS MENU ROUTINE THAT MAYBE ADAPTED AS A SUBROUTINE IN LARGERPROGRAMS. TO USE THE PROGRAM AS-IS;ENTER THE NUMBER OF MENU ITEMS; THENTHE MENU TITLE; THEN EACH MENU ITEM.TO USE THE PROGRAM AS A SUBROUTINE;SET THE VARIABLES N; M$(0); ANDM$(1-N) PROGRAMMATICALLY; RATHERTHAN WITH THE INPUT STATEMENTS.